icles can't do local sightseeing - hire a Leh-registered taxi 🏔️\\n\\nWant estimated costs for the full trip or tips on permits? 😄\"\n}\n```\n\nFrom Hyderabad to Ladakh i want transport details"}],"timestamp":1775233186834}}
