{"type":"message","id":"c88784ba","parentId":"aece7f6d","timestamp":"2026-04-03T16:20:01.496Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants transport details from Hyderabad to Ladakh. Let me compile this info.\n\nFrom the search:\n- No direct flights from Hyderabad to Leh\n- All flights have layovers (1-2 stops)\n- Travel time: 5.5 to 18+ hours depending on layovers\n- Airlines: IndiGo, Air India, SpiceJet, Vistara, Akasa Air\n- ~39 connecting flights daily\n- Book 45-60 days ahead for better fares\n\nI should also mention the road option (Hyderabad to Delhi/Mumbai then to Leh) but that's a massive journey. The best option is flying to Delhi first, then Leh.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Here's the transport from Hyderabad飞\n\n## Hyderabad → Leh (No Direct Flights)\n\n❌ **No direct flights** - you'll need a connecting flight\n\n### Best Route: Hyderabad → Delhi → Leh\n1. **Hyderabad → Delhi** (2-2.5 hrs)\n2. **Delhi → Leh** (1.5 hrs)\n\n### Airlines Available\n- IndiGo, Air India, SpiceJet, Vistara, Akasa Air\n\n### Flight Details\n- **Daily flights:** ~39 connecting options\n- **Travel time:** 6-18 hours (depends on layover)\n- **Book 45-60 days ahead** for cheaper fares\n\n---\n\n### Alternative: Road Option\nHyderabad → Delhi (via flight/train) → Delhi → Leh (flight or road)\n\nRoad from Delhi to Leh:\n- **Manali-Leh:** 2 days, opens May/June\n- **Srinagar-Leh:** 2 days, opens April\n\n---\n\n**My recommendation:** Fly Hyderabad → Delhi → Leh. Easiest and fastest ✈️\n\nWant me to check approximate flight costs?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"kilo-auto/free","usage":{"input":901,"output":511,"cacheRead":24512,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25924,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775233197786,"responseId":"gen-1775233198-lQckldCD6p0R7vItzHrn"}}
